    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK724">
<l>kaṟṟārmuṟ kaṟṟa celaccollit tāṅkaṟṟa </l>
<l>mikkāruṇ mikka koḷal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>(Ministers) should agreeably set forth their acquirements before the learned and acquire more (knowledge) from their superiors (in learning).</l>
